WEBVTT

00:01.793 --> 00:03.465
<i>Previously, on</i>
Covert Affairs...

00:03.490 --> 00:04.697
There's a conversation

00:04.698 --> 00:06.933
I've been hoping to have
with you for a while now,

00:06.934 --> 00:09.302
but I've never found
the right time to have it.

00:09.353 --> 00:11.321
We need to be
as honest as we can.

00:11.405 --> 00:13.857
It's the only way to make
this relationship work.

00:13.941 --> 00:15.025
You're a great friend,

00:15.109 --> 00:16.710
but I don't think
we should meet anymore.

00:16.744 --> 00:18.578
I love that
we've grown close again.

00:18.646 --> 00:20.831
You want to search someone's
hands for Jai's blood?

00:20.915 --> 00:22.115
Search yours.

00:22.166 --> 00:23.617
I had a meeting
with Henry Wilcox.

00:23.668 --> 00:25.752
I want to spare you
from the bloodletting

00:25.819 --> 00:26.819
about to hit Langley.

00:26.871 --> 00:28.255
Your security clearance

00:28.322 --> 00:30.290
will be dropped to a seven
until we filter the data.

00:30.341 --> 00:31.508
They requisitioned
your hard drive

00:31.592 --> 00:32.825
and downgraded
your security clearance.

00:32.877 --> 00:33.826
Henry called it.

00:33.878 --> 00:35.629
Your blood panel came back--

00:35.680 --> 00:37.430
no health issues.

00:37.498 --> 00:38.849
You're pregnant, Joan.

00:38.933 --> 00:40.767
Congratulations.

00:40.834 --> 00:42.936
- You're the Puma?
- My friends call me Teo.

00:43.003 --> 00:45.272
I suggest you two
leave Colombia.

00:45.339 --> 00:47.274
You don't want
to get lost in Medellin.

00:47.341 --> 00:49.976
The man you met, Teo--
he's Arthur's son.

00:50.027 --> 00:52.395
In the coming days,
press outlets will reveal

00:52.480 --> 00:56.366
that I have engaged
in an extramarital affair.

00:56.450 --> 00:59.286
I'm resigning my post,
effective immediately.

02:04.135 --> 02:06.269
Since when did you start
carrying on U.S. soil?

02:06.354 --> 02:09.773
Since the last time
someone broke into my kitchen.

02:12.476 --> 02:14.060
How'd you get in here?
Don't worry.

02:14.111 --> 02:15.979
I lost whatever press
was tailing me.

02:16.063 --> 02:17.743
Last thing I need right now
is to be caught

02:17.782 --> 02:19.702
having an illicit meeting
with some young blonde.

02:19.767 --> 02:22.402
Is that supposed
to be a joke?

02:22.453 --> 02:24.103
How could you do this to Joan?

02:24.155 --> 02:27.791
You don't get
to ask questions yet.

02:27.875 --> 02:30.243
We were investigating
transfer of funds

02:30.294 --> 02:34.381
from your personal account
to the Puma--a known terrorist.

02:34.448 --> 02:37.500
Henry Wilcox
gave this to you?

02:37.585 --> 02:39.786
Is, uh, this
the woman you, uh...?

02:39.837 --> 02:42.088
That I resigned over?
No, this is Teresa Hamilton.

02:42.139 --> 02:44.424
She's a cutout for the Puma.

02:44.475 --> 02:46.259
Arthur, I know
Teo is your son.

02:48.396 --> 02:51.314
What's going on here?

02:56.437 --> 02:58.822
I had no business
having a kid.

02:58.906 --> 03:00.807
I was still
basically one myself--

03:00.858 --> 03:04.611
just out of Annapolis,
my first overseas tour.

03:07.665 --> 03:10.617
And Teo's mom...

03:21.462 --> 03:24.514
her name was Ana...

03:24.598 --> 03:26.516
Ana Sofia.

03:28.302 --> 03:30.020
I didn't learn
she was pregnant

03:30.104 --> 03:34.274
until I was out
in the middle of the Pacific.

03:34.341 --> 03:36.059
If I had to do it
all over again,

03:36.143 --> 03:38.695
I would have proposed to her
right then and there

03:38.779 --> 03:41.531
and begged her to come join me
as soon as she could.

03:41.615 --> 03:45.902
But I was young and scared.

03:49.657 --> 03:51.023
So what happened?

03:51.075 --> 03:52.325
She had the baby.

03:52.376 --> 03:54.411
Her parents
became a huge obstacle.

03:54.495 --> 03:56.195
They refused
to let her marry me.

03:56.247 --> 03:58.214
They made it very difficult
for me to see my son.

03:58.299 --> 04:01.167
But, uh--
but we still managed

04:01.218 --> 04:04.504
to steal a few moments
here and there.

04:06.507 --> 04:10.060
And where's Ana Sofia now?

04:10.144 --> 04:12.378
She died.

04:14.398 --> 04:16.149
Her parents took Teo in,

04:16.216 --> 04:18.017
cut me off
from him completely.

04:18.069 --> 04:19.589
It wasn't until
they passed years later

04:19.603 --> 04:21.387
that Teo and I
were able to reconnect.

04:21.439 --> 04:23.323
And that hasn't been easy.

04:23.390 --> 04:25.892
You know, I suppose
I tried too hard

04:25.943 --> 04:28.227
to make it all up to him.

04:28.279 --> 04:30.280
There's a part of him
that keeps--

04:30.364 --> 04:32.832
that keeps pushing me away.

04:32.900 --> 04:35.735
But lately...

04:35.786 --> 04:37.003
he's become erratic.

04:37.070 --> 04:41.007
That's accurate,
with what I saw.

04:41.074 --> 04:42.792
Does Joan know about Teo?

04:42.877 --> 04:44.761
No.

04:44.845 --> 04:46.713
Why not?

04:46.764 --> 04:48.581
Joan and I had challenges
trying to start a family,

04:48.632 --> 04:51.083
and I suppose I was...

04:51.135 --> 04:54.086
You know,
I was afraid of admitting...

04:54.138 --> 04:57.857
just how much being
a father meant to me.

04:57.925 --> 05:01.060
Does Henry know Teo's my son?
He hasn't said anything to me.

05:01.112 --> 05:03.229
If he does know,
he'll do everything in his power

05:03.280 --> 05:05.198
to exploit it...

05:05.265 --> 05:06.699
to ruin me.

05:06.767 --> 05:08.768
He's gonna want to hear
what I found out in Colombia.

05:08.819 --> 05:11.538
I can try and see if he knows
the truth about Teo.

05:11.605 --> 05:13.373
Well, you can't ask him
directly.

05:13.440 --> 05:15.458
He'll have to volunteer it.

05:15.543 --> 05:17.544
What if he doesn't?

05:19.446 --> 05:21.414
Confirm everything else.

05:21.465 --> 05:23.166
Tell him
I am funding the Puma.

05:23.250 --> 05:24.250
What?

05:24.301 --> 05:26.052
Earn some trust,
some goodwill,

05:26.119 --> 05:28.254
and we'll see what he does
with the information.

05:28.305 --> 05:29.672
Henry always finds a way

05:29.757 --> 05:32.625
to profit
from other people's problems.

05:32.676 --> 05:35.962
How soon could you
arrange a meet?

05:47.992 --> 05:50.076
Thanks for meeting me
on such short notice.

05:50.143 --> 05:51.644
You said it was important.

05:51.695 --> 05:54.247
Well, I just got back
from Colombia.

05:54.314 --> 05:55.999
You verify the intel
in the file?

05:56.083 --> 05:57.500
The truth is even
more damning.

05:57.585 --> 06:00.837
The funds are being funneled
directly to Teo Braga.

06:00.921 --> 06:02.338
The Puma.

06:02.423 --> 06:04.123
What about the woman
in the photos?

06:04.175 --> 06:05.291
Got any I.D.?

06:05.342 --> 06:07.760
She's a cutout,
like you said.

06:07.828 --> 06:12.265
Arthur said her name
was Teresa Hamilton.

06:12.332 --> 06:14.551
I can't figure out
his play here.

06:14.635 --> 06:16.219
I've never had any success

06:16.303 --> 06:18.438
trying to discern
Arthur's motives.

06:18.505 --> 06:20.023
Were you able to discover

06:20.107 --> 06:23.276
the extent of Arthur's
relationship with Teo Braga?

06:26.530 --> 06:28.481
No.

06:30.534 --> 06:32.535
Well, then...

06:32.620 --> 06:34.353
Thank you for sharing.

06:34.405 --> 06:36.039
Wait.
That's it?

06:36.123 --> 06:37.857
Well, I'm sorry.

06:37.908 --> 06:40.910
You asked for the meeting.
I thought we were through.

06:40.995 --> 06:44.297
Well, what's the next thing
you want me to do?

06:44.364 --> 06:45.832
I mean, when I said I was in,
I meant it.

06:45.883 --> 06:48.134
I think you misunderstood
our last meeting.

06:48.201 --> 06:51.838
I wasn't asking you to do
anything with the file.

06:51.889 --> 06:55.225
I was simply, uh, extending
a professional courtesy.

06:55.309 --> 06:56.559
Right.
And I appreciate that.

06:56.644 --> 06:59.045
Then why'd you already
read somebody else in?

07:01.098 --> 07:04.350
You brought your boyfriend
down to Colombia.

07:06.103 --> 07:08.154
I brought my handler
to Colombia, yes.

07:08.221 --> 07:10.389
I felt I owed it to Auggie.

07:10.441 --> 07:11.441
You owed him?

07:11.525 --> 07:13.526
He's implicated
in that file.

07:13.577 --> 07:17.280
His security clearance got
dinged, just like you said.

07:17.364 --> 07:19.699
Now, Arthur...

07:19.750 --> 07:24.370
How did you know
that was gonna happen?

07:24.421 --> 07:27.373
I expected more from you.

07:37.268 --> 07:39.469
What happened?

07:39.553 --> 07:41.778
Our fish has taken the bait.

